header":"Two daughters married into the Berkshire Ingersolls","body":"Two of her eleven children — both daughters — married into the Ingersoll family of Berkshire County, Massachusetts. This is a separate Ingersoll line from the Loyalist New Haven Ingersolls who descended through the Newton-Miles line."}],"slug":"sarah-edwards-1728"}},"burialCemetery":null,"institutionsById":{},"crossConnections":[]}